<view class="page bind-page">
  <view class="eyebrow">WECHAT BINDING</view>
  <view class="page-title">绑定方式已升级</view>
  <view class="muted intro">为避免账号密码被他人用于绑定，微信绑定只允许通过本人账号生成的小程序码完成。</view>
  <view class="card form-card">
    <image class="binding-icon" src="/assets/icons/qr-scan.svg" mode="aspectFit"/>
    <view class="binding-title">请先登录 MES 账号</view>
    <view class="binding-steps">登录后进入“我的 → 账号与安全”，生成微信绑定码，再长按识别或使用另一台微信扫码确认。</view>
    <button class="primary submit" bindtap="accountLogin">前往账户密码登录</button>
    <button class="back-button" bindtap="back">返回</button>
  </view>
</view>
